{"type": "article", "id": 9833, "title": "Beautiful People 最新皮具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-21T07:08:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607114441AFUQgYMv0OyXE9VT.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t机车包不要光盯着巴黎世家了，日本品牌 Beautiful People 最近推出了一个以 Biker Jacket 为灵感的皮具系列，包括单肩包，皮夹，名片夹等等，黑色的皮具和金色的金属配件搭配在一起，营造出浓浓的街头帅气感。材质上选用的是柔软的小羊皮，即使磨损，也会散发出用旧后的特别气质。不过目前这个系列只在 Beautiful People 日本青山店和大阪店出售，感兴趣的得需要代购了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114437s06KiGPcSLkxrXUl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114438CGLb9YK2wHf0MmEg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114438o4OCMYTv3sBm6IiG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071144393MzR42lp7fTnaeyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114439ZVlz3FgKo0eTBGaW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114440Pv3n5iwexuDUJ6C7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114440EVF1qxDM3OHcevt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}